Package: FacileShine
Type: Package
Title: Shiny modules for FacileData
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Steve", "Lianoglou", , "lianoglou@dnli.com", c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Denali Therapeutics", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Provides shiny modules and gadgets for FacileData and 
    FacileAnalysisResult objects. Defines the "shine" S3 generic to invoke
    a shiny gadget for various facile objects, which will return a
    FacileGadgetResult. Calling "vizualize" on FacileGadgetResult object
    will render the main result from the gadget as an interactive htmlwidget.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    checkmate,
    FacileData,
    FacileAnalysis,
    FacileViz,
    broom,
    RColorBrewer,
    shiny (>= 1.1.0),
    shinydashboard,
    shinyjs,
    miniUI,
    promises,
    tidyr,
    V8,
    viridis
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat
License: Apache Version 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
